message: Added more background information to intro.

Disneyland Opening on ABC was not hosted by Walt. Walt attended to the festivities. Hosted by Art Linkletter who was assisted by Bob Cummings and Ronald Reagan. Cited source which was an interview of Bob Cummings himself.
Not properly sourced like the other animators on the list.

/* Career */ there was a small error saying that Iwerks came up with Mickey Mouse. This is not true. Walt came up with the original sketch, concept, and design for Mickey and then Iwerks cleaned it up and made the character more crisp.
